  "description": {
    "zh": "是啊，既然你告诉了我你的情况，那就有实际工作了。你跟我说了某个叫“Ryba”的家伙和一个竞技场管理员，我想人们叫他Ref——在竞技场外没什么大名气，但你知道，消息还是会传开的。不过，他确实越来越多地卷入外面的事件。\n\n总之，这个Ryba家伙不是普通人，他是个走私犯，在塔科夫外面有很多联系人，那些人可能会严重危及你、我、Lotus和大多数其他经销商。你的一个前PMC伙伴处理了这件事，现在不关你的事了，相信我。我们找到了他的武器藏匿点，看起来他正在为某件大事做准备，你几乎能在那里找到一切！机枪、狙击步枪、火箭筒、大量爆炸物和成箱的穿甲弹药，这家伙懂武器。\n\n嗯，我需要有人把这些装备的一部分放到特定地点，你能做吗？确保你带个大背包。我建议你向Lotus寻求帮助，我想她现在还保管着剩下的装备。",
    "en": "Yeah, now that you told me about your situation, there is actual work. You told me about some \"Ryba\" dude and an Arena administrator, I think people call him Ref - Not a big name outside the Arena but you know, word still gets around. However, he does have his involvement in more and more events out here.\n\nAnyway, this Ryba fella wasn't just someone, he was a smuggler and he had a lot of contacts outside Tarkov, contacts with people that could seriously endanger you, me, Lotus and most other dealers. One of your ex-PMC buddies took care of it, it won't be any of your concern now, believe me. We found his weapon stash, looks like he was preparing for something big, you could find everything there! Machine guns, sniper rifles, rocket launchers, loads of explosives and a ton of crates filled with armor-piercing ammunition, this guy knew weapons.\n\nWell I need someone to drop off some of this gear at certain locations, can you do that? Make sure you bring a big bag. I suggest you ask Lotus for help, I think she still has the rest of the gear in her possession at the moment."
  },
